article.headline: Dinkins scores 22, Canisius defeats Siena 73-64

images.name: Canisius Golden Griffins vs. Siena Saints: Game Highlights
images.caption: Canisius Golden Griffins vs. Siena Saints: Game Highlights

article.story: ALBANY, N.Y. -- — Tre Dinkins scored 22 points and Canisius beat Siena 73-64 on Sunday. Dinkins added six rebounds for the Golden Griffins (10-15, 5-10 Metro Atlantic Athletic Conference). Frank Mitchell went 6 of 8 from the field to add 12 points. Cam Palesse went 4 of 10 from the field to finish with 10 points. The Saints (4-22, 3-12) were led in scoring by Giovanni Emejuru, who finished with 23 points and 14 rebounds. Siena also got 12 points each from Michael Ojo and Mason Courtney. ------ The Associated Press created this story using technology provided by Data Skrive and data from Sportradar.
